        <div class="sam-case-solution__item">
          <h3 class="sam-case-solution__item-title">Continuous monitoring</h3>
          <p class="sam-case-solution__item-desc">Every connected pump monitored 24/7. SAM4 detects bearing degradation, blockages, cavitation, and efficiency losses as they develop — weeks before failure.</p>
